media_attachments.description:
A screenshot of code showing a lightweight dependency interface for a speech client. The code reads as follows:

// A lightweight interface to abstract over a speech
// recognition client.
struct SpeechClient {
  var requestAuthorization: @Sendable
    () async -> SFSpeechRecognizerAuthorizationStatus
  var start: @Sendable 
    () -> AsyncThrowingStream<String, Error>
}
